  "detailed_description": "Ouros is a calming puzzle game about forming beautiful curves in a serene space. Find your flow as you nudge, bend, and stretch curves into pleasing shapes. <br><br>The goal is simple. Align the curve with the targets, then watch the orb gracefully glide through them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/6855cc7d33eda591263398d3ca7973e8.poster.avif?t=1773176501\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/6855cc7d33eda591263398d3ca7973e8.webm?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/6855cc7d33eda591263398d3ca7973e8.mp4?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With over 120 handcrafted puzzles to solve, Ouros invites you to discover the inherent mathematical beauty of its world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/9fef93844a339f2f97fd41ea6bc4d432.poster.avif?t=1773176501\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/9fef93844a339f2f97fd41ea6bc4d432.webm?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/9fef93844a339f2f97fd41ea6bc4d432.mp4?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An original spline-based control scheme<br></li><li>Lush visuals and soothing soundscapes that dynamically respond to the forms you create<br></li><li>A flexible level progression and hint system that let you play at your own pace<br></li><li>A fluid gameplay experience free of timers, scores, or dexterity requirements<br></li><li>Touchscreen support for Steam Deck. Mouse & Keyboard support for PCs</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Ouros is a calming puzzle game about forming beautiful curves in a serene space. Find your flow as you nudge, bend, and stretch curves into pleasing shapes. <br><br>The goal is simple. Align the curve with the targets, then watch the orb gracefully glide through them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/6855cc7d33eda591263398d3ca7973e8.poster.avif?t=1773176501\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/6855cc7d33eda591263398d3ca7973e8.webm?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/6855cc7d33eda591263398d3ca7973e8.mp4?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With over 120 handcrafted puzzles to solve, Ouros invites you to discover the inherent mathematical beauty of its world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/9fef93844a339f2f97fd41ea6bc4d432.poster.avif?t=1773176501\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/9fef93844a339f2f97fd41ea6bc4d432.webm?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452920/extras/9fef93844a339f2f97fd41ea6bc4d432.mp4?t=1773176501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An original spline-based control scheme<br></li><li>Lush visuals and soothing soundscapes that dynamically respond to the forms you create<br></li><li>A flexible level progression and hint system that let you play at your own pace<br></li><li>A fluid gameplay experience free of timers, scores, or dexterity requirements<br></li><li>Touchscreen support for Steam Deck. Mouse & Keyboard support for PCs</li></ul>",
